{"tid":1422913,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"天水圍勇武真係好高質","createTime":"2019-08-06T12:20:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T13:20:26.000Z","uid":70745,"like":56,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a88a8771d7e89682f098409c663c8efd4fac7590","tid":1422913,"uid":70745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:20:49.000Z","msg":"岩岩睇到個post話要比勇武收光環，所以想講番琴日既所見所聞。<br />\n<br />\n話說琴晚我企左係天盛迴旋處附近，見到有個阿姨要係狗屋同街市中間個條路出去，但個陣有人掉緊石仔，啲狗又放緊催淚彈，所以好危險。有兩個勇武同佢講好危險唔好去，阿姨一意孤行，跟住果兩個上左裝既勇武，一個用盾係阿姨身邊護住行，一個用遮擋住，仲叫天台隻狗唔好射，有路人係到。我見到真係哇一聲，但太遠又冇裝唔可以上前影低。<br />\n<br />\n我冇圖，但100% real。希望琴晚個兩位師兄可以睇到，真係好多謝你地，你地真係好高汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dd558835201ca0371d1181c2d105ff53f63d3cd","tid":1422913,"uid":70745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:24:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a3d6535fcf3255bbc479252be11b71af8298bd88","tid":1422913,"uid":70745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:24:23.000Z","msg":"希望琴晚係天水圍既街坊可以睇到"},{"pid":"8a7d64a45386f106394a50d10a2174774e2b4460","tid":1422913,"uid":70745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:25:01.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"8a79586c837b60d8dfcd7b57e0076a785944b67b","tid":1422913,"uid":70745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:25:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd567261f47e3ced7e19e05f0d1bf9ac5de64cb0","tid":1422913,"uid":70745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:26:10.000Z","msg":"睇完幫手推"},{"pid":"fd517bae19549be4cafb078160254799abd06919","tid":1422913,"